text.tspan: Share of women in parliament, 1900 to 2022
Percentage of seats in lower or single chamber of the legislature held by women, weighted by countries' populations.
Source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
